{"tid":1137621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"戇鳩港豬自己無民主但走去批判人地泰國極權 叫香港人守住 守乜柒？","createTime":"2019-05-04T02:49:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T05:15:26.000Z","uid":92376,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"24366d1106e7c279b73d5cab3f6bd0ea7adfe239","tid":1137621,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T02:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nag52JR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnag52JR.png&h=894e284a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲高高在上以為自己大香港係清泉？<br />\n柒唔撚柒啲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫香港守住 好似泰國衰過你咁<br />\n起碼人地有民主有政黨制先<br />\n投票都投得開心啲<br />\n而王室係人地國民文化 精神象徵<br />\n侮辱王室大不敬而要重罰就講到係咩極權<br />\n<br />\n好就算當係極權 豪比你<br />\n不過點都好過香港 無呢啲王室都大把野愁啦<br />\n睇住逃犯條例過左全香港攬炒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲好意思話人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4acc5022eae469d1ca40a5bfe55308164b4413e6","tid":1137621,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T02:57:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5813cabaa53d8b7e1199be4